ygData.messageBody:
I think its the generic -- Vox chases everyone out of the zone due
to someone's mistake or misfortune, then the entire group is
"spanked". Although sometimes spanking is not all that bad, but
lets not go there.


> > Sounds like you got spanked to me even if mistakes were made you still got
> > spanked.
>
> Well, I didn't die. So if dying is part of getting spanked, then
> it didn't happen bro.
>
> Harmonic
